<h1 itemprop="name">10 best cruise lines for every type of traveler, from adventurers to families</h1>
<div class="subheader-article">The best vacations for solo travelers to social butterflies</div>	
    <div class="row">
    <div class="small-4 medium-2 large-2 columns show-for-medium-up"><a href="/local-experts/danielle-bauter/"><img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAGQAAABkCAYAAABw4pVUAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAADsMAAA7DAcdvqGQAAAA+SURBVHhe7cExAQAAAMKg9U9tCy8gAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAADgqAacpAAB5eVcggAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="//img1.10bestmedia.com/Images/Photos/372752/Bauter-Headshot_14_100x100.JPG" alt="Danielle Bauter" class="expert lazy" width="81" height="81" /></a></div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-10 large-5 columns">
    <p class="show-for-small-only small sans-serif-heading"><time datetime="2024-5-6">May 6, 2024</time> // By <a href="/local-experts/danielle-bauter/" rel="author">Danielle Bauter</a></p>
    <p class="show-for-medium-up sans-serif-heading">By <a href="/local-experts/danielle-bauter/" rel="author">Danielle Bauter</a><br /> 	<time class="main-time" datetime="2024-5-6">May 6, 2024</time></p>
